original_title: The Grapes of Wrath: Seems Like Fate
overview: This collection of 10 music videos produced between 1984 and 1992 charts the creative growth of folk rockers the Grapes of Wrath and takes a look back at some of the band's most prolific years. Selections include "You May Be Right," "All the Things I Wasn't," "What Was Going Through My Head," "Do You Want to Tell Me," "I Am Here," "Peace of Mind" and "A Fishing Tale," plus a bonus offering of the 2000 video "Black Eye."
title: The Grapes of Wrath: Seems Like Fate
